    "body": "I'm thinking about write a new formatter (likely going to be a future addition to cython-lint) and in doing so I thought about ensuring that the current `CodeWriter` has it's current scope expanded by looking into some unimplemented stuff. Luckily I have already found a few and I've written another test module since so I could attempt to unit test for missing items.",
    "closed_at": null,
